// 3. Removed `payable` from `Collect` function and used `require` to ensure sufficient balance and unlocked time
// 4. Used `transfer` instead of `call` in `Collect` function 
// 5. Added `memory` to `Message` struct in `Log` contract and initialized `LastMsg` in `AddMessage` function